Providence strangely directed Imogen's steps to the dwelling of her two brothers , who had been stolen away in their infancy . 
At the cave where these youths dwelt it was Imogen's fortune to arrive . 
Seeing this cave , she entered , hoping to find someone within of whom she could procure food . 
Bellarius entered the cave first , and seeing Imogen , stopped them , saying 'Come not in yet it eats our victuals , or I should think it was a fairy . 
'What is the matter , sir ? said the young men . 
'By Jupiter , said Bellarius again , 'there is an angel in the cave , or if not , an earthly paragon . 
So beautiful did Imogen look in her boy's apparel . 
