When power bowed to flattery , honour was bound to plainness . 
For Lear's threats , what could he do to him , whose life was already at his service ? That should not hinder duty from speaking . 
And Cordelia with a heavy heart departed , for she knew the cunning of her sisters , and she wished her father in better hands than she was about to leave him in . 
Cordelia was no sooner gone , than the devilish dispositions of her sisters began to show themselves in their true colours . 
