Escalus said 'The duke is in us , and we will hear you . 
Then , to the amazement of all present , and to the utter confusion of Angelo , the supposed friar threw off his disguise , and they saw it was the duke himself . 
The duke first addressed Isabel . 
He said to her 'Come hither , Isabel . 
Your friar is now your prince , but with my habit I have not changed my heart . 
I am still devoted to your service . 
'O give me pardon , said Isabel , 'that I , your vassal , have employed and troubled your unknown sovereignty . 
