Immediate sentence and death is all the grace I beg . 
The duke replied 'Angelo , thy faults are manifest . 
Should Isabel kneel down to beg for mercy , her brother's ghost would break his paved bed , and take her hence in horror . 
Still Mariana said 'Isabel , sweet Isabel , do but kneel by me , hold up your hand , say nothing ! I will speak all . 
They say , best men are moulded out of faults , and for the most part become much the better for being a little bad . 
I partly think a due sincerity governed his deeds , till he did look on me . 
