Say you will be mine , and he shall be my brother too . 
Angelo remembered , when dressed in a little brief authority , how hard his heart had been , and felt how sweet is mercy . 
The duke commanded Claudio to marry Juliet , and offered himself again to the acceptance of Isabel , whose virtuous and noble conduct had won her prince's heart . 
And the mercy loving duke long reigned with his beloved Isabel , the happiest of husbands and of princes . 
