He reached Verona at midnight , and found the churchyard , in the midst of which was situated the ancient tomb of the Capulets . 
But the count in scorn refused his warning , and laid hands on him as a felon , which Romeo resisting , they fought , and Paris fell . 
The watch by this time had come up to the place . 
The friar had been apprehended by some of the watch , coming from the churchyard , trembling , sighing , and weeping , in a suspicious manner . 
